OASR_128.Description: Sum of scores of items 8-Can’t get mind off thoughts, 9-Can’t sit still, 11-Too dependent, 13-Cries a lot, 14-Too concerned about getting old, 21-Worries about future, 23-Feels too guilty, 26-Fears, 28-Fears doing bad, 32-Feels worthless, 34-Restless, fidgety, 40-Nervous, tense, 42-Lacks self-confidence, 45-Fearful, anxious, 47-Guilty conscience, 62-Self-conscious, 91-Thinks about past too much, 93-Unhappy, sad, depressed, 100-Worries a lot, 109-Concerned about death. | Calculation = [OASR_08a] + [OASR_9a] + [OASR_11] + [OASR_13] + [OASR_14] + [OASR_21] + [OASR_23] + [OASR_26a] + [OASR_28] + [OASR_32] + [OASR_34] + [OASR_40] + [OASR_42] + [OASR_45] + [OASR_47] + [OASR_62] + [OASR_91] + [OASR_93] + [OASR_100] + [OASR_109]

OASR_129.Description: Sum of scores of items 51-Worries about appearance, 72-Worries about family, 89-Concerned being neat, clean, 90-Trouble sleeping, 101-Wakes up too early, 102-Worries too much about health, 117-Gets too tired, 121-Burdensome. | Calculation = [OASR_51] + [OASR_72] + [OASR_89] + [OASR_90] + [OASR_101] + [OASR_102] + [OASR_117] + [OASR_121]

OASR_130.Description: Sum of scores of items 5-Too much medication, 33-Feels sick a lot, 46-Feels dizzy, 49a-Aches, pains, 49b-Headaches, 49c-Nausea, feels sick, 49d-Eye problems, 49e-Skin problems, 49f-Stomachaches, 49g-Vomiting, 49h-Hear pounding, 49i-Numbness, 49j-Short of breath, 103-Nightmares. | Calculation = [OASR_05] + [OASR_33] + [OASR_46] + [OASR_49a] + [OASR_49b] + [OASR_49c] + [OASR_49d1] + [OASR_49e] + [OASR_49f] + [OASR_49g] + [OASR_49h] + [OASR_49i] + [OASR_49j] + [OASR_103]

OASR_131.Description: Sum of scores of items 3-Trouble getting things done, 10-Too dependent, 16-Sits around, 29-Trouble preparing meals, 54-Poor work performance, 55-Clumsy, 68-Sleeps more than other people, 92-Lacks energy, 104-Trouble dressing self, 106-Trouble bathing, grooming, 111-Soiling. | Calculation = [OASR_03] + [OASR_10] + [OASR_16] + [OASR_29] + [OASR_54] + [OASR_55] + [OASR_68] + [OASR_92] + [OASR_104] + [OASR_106] + [OASR_111]

OASR_132.Description: Sum of scores of items 7-Can’t concentrate, 12-Confused, 20-Forgets names, 52-Fails to finish, 69-Trouble making decisions, 70-Trouble talking, 110-Trouble remembering, 114-Forgets, 122-Worries about memory. | Calculation = [OASR_07] + [OASR_12] + [OASR_20] + [OASR_52] + [OASR_69] + [OASR_70] + [OASR_110] + [OASR_114] + [OASR_122]

OASR_133.Description: Sum of scores of items 24-Jealous of others, 27-Poor relations with neighbors, 30-Feels no one cares, 31- Others out to get him/her, 36-Hears sounds, voices, 38,-Rather be alone, 41-Twitching, 57-Repeats acts, 58-Trouble making friends, 60-Secretive, 61-See things, 74-Strange behavior, 75-Strange ideas, 77-Mood changes, 99-Withdrawn. | Calculation = [OASR_24] + [OASR_27] + [OASR_30] + [OASR_31] + [OASR_36a] + [OASR_38] + [OASR_41a] + [OASR_57a] + [OASR_58] + [OASR_60] + [OASR_61a] + [OASR_74a] + [OASR_75a] + [OASR_77] + [OASR_99]

OASR_134.Description: Sum of scores of items 2-Argues a lot, 15-Mean to others, 18-Demands attention, 19-Damages things, 22-Doesn’t get along, 25-Gets along badly with family, 35-Likes things own way, 37-Impulsive, 39-Does things others don’t like, 43-Not liked by others, 59-Screams a lot, 65-ShowsOff/Showing off, clowning, 67-Irresponsible, 76-Stubborn, 79-Suspicious, 83-Talks too much, 84-Irritates others, 85-Loses temper, 86-Thinks about sex too much, 94-Louder than others. | Calculation = [OASR_02] + [OASR_15] + [OASR_18] + [OASR_19] + [OASR_22] + [OASR_25] + [OASR_35] + [OASR_37] + [OASR_39] + [OASR_43] + [OASR_59] + [OASR_65] + [OASR_67] + [OASR_76] + [OASR_79] + [OASR_83] + [OASR_84] + [OASR_85] + [OASR_86] + [OASR_94]

OASR_135.Description: Sum of scores of items 17-Harms self 48-Gets too tired, 49k-Other physical problems, 50-Attacks people, 53-Enjoys little, 56-Avoids talking, 63-Being punished, 66-Too shy, timid, 73-Steals, 80-Drinks too much, 81-Thinks suicide, 82-Trouble with the law, 87-Threatens people, 97-Can’t succeed, 105-Dislikes using phone, 115-Bored. | Calculation = [OASR_17] + [OASR_48] + [OASR_49k1] + [OASR_50] + [OASR_53] + [OASR_56] + [OASR_63] + [OASR_66] + [OASR_73] + [OASR_80] + [OASR_81] + [OASR_82a] + [OASR_87] + [OASR_97] + [OASR_105] + [OASR_115]

OASR_136.Description: “Critical” items were determined by a group of highly experienced psychiatrist and psychologist from 10 cultures who identified ASEBA adult problem items that are very consistent with DSM-IV diagnostic categories. They also rated each ASEBA problem item according to whether “it refers to problems that clinicians may be particularly concerned about, whether or not the items are included in diagnostic criteria.” Sum of scores of items 5-Too much medication, 7-Can’t concentrate,  8- Can’t get mind off thoughts 12-Confused, 13-Cries a lot, 17-Harms self, 23-Feels too guilty, 26-Fears, 31- Others out to get him/her, 32-Feels worthless, 36-Hears sounds, voices, 45-Fearful, 47-Guilty conscience, 49j-Short of Breath, 50-Attacks people, 53-Enjoys little, 57-Repeats acts, 61-Sees things, 67-Irresponsible, 69-Trouble making decisions, 74-Strange behavior, 75-Strange ideas, 80-Drinks too much, 81-Thinks suicide, 82-Trouble with the law, 90-Trouble sleeping, 93-Unhappy, sad, depressed, 101-Wakes up too early, 110-Trouble remembering, 114-Forgets, and 121-Burdensome. | Calculation = [OASR_08a] + [OASR_13] + [OASR_23] + [OASR_26a] + [OASR_32] + [OASR_45] + [OASR_47] + [OASR_93] + [OASR_90] + [OASR_101] + [OASR_121] + [OASR_05] + [OASR_49j] + [OASR_07] + [OASR_12] + [OASR_69] + [OASR_110] + [OASR_114] + [OASR_31] + [OASR_36a] + [OASR_57a] + [OASR_61a] + [OASR_74a] + [OASR_75a] + [OASR_67] + [OASR_17] + [OASR_50] + [OASR_53] + [OASR_80] + [OASR_81] + [OASR_82a]

OASR_137.Description: Sum of Thought Problems, Attention Problems, Other Problems, Internalizing Behaviors and Externalizing Behaviors. A participant’s Total Problems score can range from 0 (if the respondent scored every problem 0) to 246 (if the respondent scored every problem 2). | Calculation = [OASR_128] + [OASR_129] + [OASR_130] + [OASR_131] + [OASR_132] + [OASR_133] + [OASR_134] + [OASR_135]
